title: Wipes
features: PACK CONTENTS: 80 gentle, thick wet wipes perfect for delicate skin, featuring safe and natural ingredients for everyday use
SKIN-FRIENDLY FORMULA: Contains soothing Aloe Vera and nourishing Vitamin E to help maintain soft, healthy skin
CONVENIENT PACKAGING: Resealable pack design helps maintain moisture and freshness while allowing easy dispensing of wipes
VERSATILE USE: Suitable for all skin types and gentle enough for daily cleansing and personal hygiene routines
QUALITY FEATURES: Extra thick, soft texture wipes that are durable yet gentle, providing thorough cleansing without irritation
description: Product description Experience ultimate comfort with these gentle, thick wet wipes that are perfect for delicate skin. Each pack contains 80 premium wipes enriched with soothing Aloe Vera and Vitamin E to help maintain skin health. The wipes feature a convenient resealable closure to maintain freshness and prevent drying out. These generously-sized wipes are soft, strong, and gentle enough for daily use. The unique formula contains safe and natural ingredients, making them suitable for all skin types. The practical packaging design makes these wipes ideal for both home use and travel. Whether for personal care, baby care, or general cleaning, these wipes offer reliable performance with a feather-soft touch that's kind to your skin. Safety Warning Wet wipes See packaging
